@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC004 Quên mật khẩu

actor "User" as Actor
boundary "ForgotPassUI" as UI
control "AuthController" as Controller
control "EmailService" as EmailService
entity "UserAccount" as UserDB

Actor -> UI : 1. Nhập Email cần lấy lại MK
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. requestResetPass(email)
activate Controller
Controller -> UserDB : 3. checkEmail()
activate UserDB
UserDB --> Controller : exists
deactivate UserDB
Controller -> EmailService : 4. sendOTP()
activate EmailService
EmailService --> Controller : sent
deactivate EmailService
Controller --> UI : 5. Show OTP form
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 6. Yêu cầu nhập OTP & Pass mới
deactivate UI

Actor -> UI : 7. Nhập OTP + Pass mới
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 8. resetPass(email, otp, newPass)
activate Controller
Controller -> Controller : 9. verifyOTP()
Controller -> UserDB : 10. updatePassword(newPass)
activate UserDB
UserDB --> Controller : success
deactivate UserDB
Controller --> UI : 11. success
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 12. Báo thành công, điều hướng Login
deactivate UI
@enduml